OL,3,CCould 'mental health ambulances' help
OL,4,Ckeep patients out of hospital?
OL,6,FMental health patients are avoiding
OL,7,Funnecessary trips to hospital thanks
OL,8,Fto new specialist ambulances,
OL,9,Faccording to South Western Ambulance
OL,10,FService.
OL,12,FIts fleet of seven vehicles were
OL,13,Fpiloted last year and introduced
OL,14,Fpermanently in February 2025.
OL,16,FThe trust says already more than 700
OL,17,Fpatients have avoided being taken to a
OL,18,Fhospital emergency department as a
OL,19,Fresult.
