OL,3,CCould 'mental health ambulances' help
OL,4,Ckeep patients out of hospital?
OL,6,FThe ambulances, which look like small
OL,7,Fminibuses, are staffed by mental
OL,8,Fhealth specialists and designed to
OL,9,Foffer a calming space for assessing
OL,10,Fpatients.
OL,12,FThey are roomier than a car, but don't
OL,13,Fhave medical equipment on display like
OL,14,Fstandard ambulances. Most patients
OL,15,Fthat the ambulances attend are
OL,16,Factively suicidal.
OL,18,F"The main thing we need to establish
OL,19,Fquickly is a rapport," says the
OL,20,Fambulance trust's head of mental
OL,21,Fhealth, Matt Truscott.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
