OL,3,CCould 'mental health ambulances' help
OL,4,Ckeep patients out of hospital?
OL,6,FThe rest go to A&E - a potentially
OL,7,Fstressful process which can take
OL,8,Fseveral hours and which often ends in
OL,9,Fa patient being released to the same
OL,10,Ftype of community-based service anyway.
OL,12,FIf you are struggling there is help
OL,13,Favailable. Call the free Papyrus
OL,14,Fhelpline on 0800 068 4141 or click
OL,15,Fhere for websites that can provide you
OL,16,Fwith support.
