OL,3,CCould 'mental health ambulances' help
OL,4,Ckeep patients out of hospital?
OL,6,FThe mental health charity SANE
OL,7,Fsupports the initiative but says it
OL,8,Fneeds to be backed up by more crisis
OL,9,Fbeds for mental health care. "If you
OL,10,Fcan avoid the A&E admission you may
OL,11,Fget over that (mental health) crisis,"
OL,12,Fsays the charity's chief executive,
OL,13,FMarjorie Wallace.
OL,15,F"But we'd like to see that backed by
OL,16,Fmore crisis beds being available if
OL,17,Fthey are too ill. You can't just have
OL,18,Fa team go out and sit with someone if
OL,19,Fthey are saying they are going to
OL,20,F(take their own life)."
