OL,3,CCould 'mental health ambulances' help
OL,4,Ckeep patients out of hospital?
OL,6,FMental health calls to South Western
OL,7,FAmbulance Service have gone up 83% in
OL,8,Fsix years, partly because police
OL,9,Fforces no longer deal with as many.
OL,11,FBut specialist mental health
OL,12,Fambulances are scarce - the vehicle we
OL,13,Flooked at, based at Taunton Ambulance
OL,14,FStation, is the only one in Somerset.
